name: Ruffle Tiered Dress
description: Olive green strapless linen dress with ruffled tier design.  Comes with mahoghany colored stretch faux leather belt.  100% linen.  Made in the USA.  Machine wash gentle cycle.  This item runs a bit small. Comes in sizes XL, 2X and 3X.

name: Flutter Sleeve Blouse
description: Rich turquoise colored cotton flutter sleeve top, with floral rhinestone appliqued neckline. Elasticized drop waist band.  100% cotton.  Made in China.  Hand wash.  Sizes 2X and 3X.

name: Metallic Diamond Top
description: Red 3/4 sleeve poly/rayon blend top with built in camisole.  Metallic diamond embelishment on the bottom of top.  Fantastic drape.  Made in the USA.  Machine wash gentle cycle,or hand wash.  Sizes 1X - 3X.

name: Metal Nail Head Trim Dress
description: Eggplant colored dress with metal nail head trim can be worn as a top, or for the more adventurous as a dress.  Cotton/poly blend. Made in China.  Handwash.  Dress is 35" long from top to bottom.  Comes in sizes 1X - 3X.

name: Leather And Chain Top
description: Dark fuschia short sleeve top with faux leather patches and chains.  This top is accentuated with 2 leather like patches with metal studs. 5 dark colored chains are attached to each patch.  100% rayon provides a nice drape across the body.  Drop waist with slight ruffle hem. Made in the USA.  Hand wash.  30" long.  Sizes 1X - 3X.
